title: 111_s2071
content: CERTAIN IMAGING COLORANTS. Subchapter II of chapter 99 of the Harmonized Tariff Schedule of the United States is amended by inserting new headings. "9902.01.00 Aryl substituted pyrazonyl sodium salt (PMN No. P03-78) and substituted naphthalene potassium/sodium salt (PMN No. P04-390) provided for in subheading 3215.11.00." "9902.01.00 Copper phthalocyanine substituted with sulphonic acids and alkyl sulphonoamides, sodium/ammonium salts (PMN No. P02-893) provided for in subheading 3215.19.00." No. 90295-11-7, 9902.01.00 - Copper phthalocyanine substituted with sulphonic acids and alkyl sulphonoamides, sodium salt (CAS No.) and substituted naphthalenylazol alkoxyl phenyl azo carboxyphenylene, lithium salt (PMN No. P-00-351) provided for in subheading 3215.19.00. On or before 12/31/2011. 9902.01.00 - Copper phthalocyanine substituted with sulphonic acids and sulphonoamides, sodium salts (CAS No. 90295-11-7) and substituted napthtylene aminoalkyl triazinediyl bis substituted phenylene azo bis, sodium salt (CAS No. 50925-42-3) provided for in subheading 3215.19.00. On or before 12/31/2011. Substituted napthtylene aminoalkyl triazinediyl bis substituted phenylene azo bis, sodium salt (CAS No. 50925-42-3) provided for in subheading 3215.11.00. Aryl [Substituted phenylazo] pyridine, sodium/lithium salt (PMN No. P-02-234) provided for in subheading 3215.19.00. The effective date for the amendment applies to articles entered or withdrawn from warehouse for consumption after the 15th day following the enactment of the Act.
